items.badge_description: We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 60 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 13! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.checkin_comment: A touch too hoppy for my usual taste but there's a lot going on outside that. lightly orangy with a lovely aftertaste. bitter at the end
Quite hoppy. Smells a bit like socks. Not really a fan.
Hoppy and delicious! More fruity, not piney, but yes! Drink me!
